OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny heavy
OL,6,Fand thundery showers dying out this
OL,7,Fevening. Then the rest of the night
OL,8,Fwill be will be dry with variable
OL,9,Famounts of cloud.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FMainly dry in the morning
OL,12,Fwith bright spells. Becoming cloudier
OL,13,Fin the afternoon with showers
OL,14,Fspreading from the west. Breezy along
OL,15,Fthe west coast. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
